name: BurrowFall
description:
Game made for the 2023 Global Game Jam

Fall your way down the rabbit hole while avoiding the roots as long as possible. 

Move the rabbit with WASD or Arrow keys.

Try to beat your high score!

Developer

Miguel Monteiro
